name: Wonka Classic Bar
description: Classic Wonka chocolate bar, designed by no other than Willy Wonka. This chocolate is best known for its rich taste and creamy texture that melts perfectly in your mouth.

name: Wonka Waterfall Bar
description: Try out out latest chocolate - Wonka's waterfall chocolate! With a perfect mix of white, black and milk chocolate, it will surely blow your mind away!

name: Wonka Caramel Bar
description: Try out the best caramel chocolate in the world! The center of this chocolate is flowing with caramel filling which will make you crave for more...

name: Wonka Chilly Chocolate Bar
description: Wonka Chilly Chocolate Bar will surely make you fall in love with chocolate all over again. The creamy white chocolate mixed with the secret ingridient which gives you the chills will make this your favorite chocolate.

name: Wonka Nutty Chocolate
description: The best chocolate with nuts on the market. Designed by WIlly Wonka in the beggining of 2000s.

name: Top Cacao
description: Our premium cacao product boasts an exquisite, velvety texture with a rich, authentic flavor. Handcrafted to perfection, it offers an indulgent, luxurious experience, delivering the pure essence of exceptional quality cacao.
